      <title>星巴克9美元咖啡争议：当“可负担”遭遇质疑，咖啡涨价与消费降级正在重塑行业</title>
      <link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/xing-ba-ke-9mei-yuan-ka-pei-zheng-yi-dang-ke-fu-da/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 19:55:39 +0800</pubDate>
